===Noun===
'''loan'''

#A sum of money that someone [[borrow]]s from another with the condition that it be repaid at a later date (usually with [[interest]]).  Sometimes [[collateral]] is required in case the [[borrower]] cannot repay their [[debt]].

====Translation====
*[[Dutch]]: [[lening]] ''f''
*[[French]]: [[emprunt]] ''m''
